The PCF Isolation Segment tile is intended for use with Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) v.1.10 and later. To install a PCF Isolation Segment, you must first install PCF v1.10.

For more information, see [Installing PCF Isolation Segment](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/opsguide/installing-pcf-is.html).

